article_text:
Oskaloosa, IA (52577)

Today

Partly cloudy with afternoon showers or thunderstorms. A few storms may be severe. High 84F. Winds SSW at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 40%..

Tonight

Thunderstorms likely this evening. Then the chance of scattered thunderstorms overnight. A few storms may be severe. Low 63F. Winds SSE at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 80%.

article_metadata.author: ANGIE HOLLAND Herald staff writer

og.description: OSKALOOSA—The Smokey Row was buzzing not only with caffeine, but with interest in meeting and listening to Democratic presidential candidate Martin O'Malley speak.
og.title: Presidental candidate O'Malley visits Oskaloosa
